"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"The lack of post stats is a common feature request of Mirror, in this article I’ll introduce a solution for this.\\n\\nThe theory is simple: Mirror allows you to add image via a remote url, and when the post is visited, the image will be loaded from that url, so the server hosts the image knowns how many users visited the post.\\n\\nOne service provides such analytics via image is [GoatCounter](https://www.goatcounter.com/), we’ll use it as an example:\\n\\nFirst, sign up GoatCounter:\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/jJtnSes6WnMN-fGqpJOKP.png?height=674&width=1700)\\n\\nRemember the code you input, it’ll be used in the following steps. For example, the code I choose is wong2, so I’ll be redirected to https://wong2.goatcounter.com\\n\\nThen you can add analytics image to your mirror post. The image endpoint format is https://\\\\[my-code\\\\].goatcounter.com/count?p=\\\\[path\\\\] .\\n\\nSo if I’d like to add analytic to this post, I can use a image url like: https://wong2.goatcounter.com/count?p=/mirror-post-stats\\n\\nEmbed an image at the end of your post like this:\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/4qx5VtCJfcQXN-aBjaNOm.png?height=1186&width=974)\\n\\nAnd you’re done! You can go to GoatCounter to see analytics of post views now.\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/ZoGA6GfQAOsg1IQTuzlnM.png?height=1096&width=2754)\\n\\n![](https://wong2.goatcounter.com/count?p=/mirror-post-stats)\\n\\n\",\"timestamp\":1642053295,\"title\":\"A method to add visit stats for Mirror posts\"},\"digest\":\"QFdFSEPeRErvuKKQWU5uGhcQQd8737gZlmF0JC1B8pU\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0xE6EF1843DbC51C5f15fB6e6db7168ACFe84F34f1\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"3h6wj-zi-IgjhnJst6KwHGIVNL7l3AodQfcJBgTRK2Y\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"xCNFb939rIXbh42NA-ZoE70MfoiEL6kNwZe8zVvHzNY\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"Kb7sS7Qsd9dmxVRhb3o0vHI9C3HQ8CVFujX2TSiiHQK1wgy6ZRPKgBtCx25-CFTZsFyS9tKEmJ4JdY0Zh8Q70w\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x9b48e514e4595e1b57c9222d638b073b1636b9a7edb4dcf17b4b7247d1f36e184a3129a66a5b73672b54e6c3fb47051ba0417f75cf6825ea14ebad27640a200b1c\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"3h6wj-zi-IgjhnJst6KwHGIVNL7l3AodQfcJBgTRK2Y\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"xCNFb939rIXbh42NA-ZoE70MfoiEL6kNwZe8zVvHzNY\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"XhM6k8pBMcugSkRqyGkeZNjcfwwfd0ilaJoVqzw5UxI\"}"